nodes.text: Hi, just picked up my prescription and the pharmacist talk to me and told me about side effects of blood clotting should I still take my baby aspirin I was diagnosed with anti-phospholipid cardio Lapin years ago that why I take the baby aspirin. Is that a concern for this medication, also considering there may be side effects is it OK if I start the medication on MM/DD/YYYY as I need to work this weekend? Also, is it possible to get an Imodium prescription in case I do experience the diarrhea  Thank you, Person1
